   "source": [
    "## Visualize"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "85579924",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from chemml.visualization import scatter2D, SavePlot, decorator\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "257b6a43",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "The Plot has been saved at:  ./images/Parity.png\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "df = pd.DataFrame()\n",
    "df[\"Actual\"] = np.random.random(50)\n",
    "df[\"Predicted\"] = np.random.random(50)\n",
    "sc = scatter2D('b', marker='.')\n",
    "fig = sc.plot(dfx=df, dfy=df, x=\"Actual\", y=\"Predicted\")\n",
    "\n",
    "dec = decorator(title='Actual vs. Predicted',xlabel='Actual', ylabel='Predicted',\n",
    "                xlim= (0,1), ylim=(0,1), grid=True,\n",
    "                grid_color='g', grid_linestyle=':', grid_linewidth=0.5)\n",
    "fig = dec.fit(fig)\n",
    "# print(type(fig))\n",
    "sa=SavePlot(filename='Parity',output_directory='images',\n",
    "            kwargs={'facecolor':'w','dpi':330,'pad_inches':0.1, 'bbox_inches':'tight'})\n",
    "sa.save(obj=fig)\n",
    "fig.show()"
   ]
  }
 ],
